{"tid":1638033,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑香港的股市和樓市，皆有強大的維穩力量支撐","createTime":"2019-10-08T07:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T09:22:49.000Z","uid":149978,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"bee0a145054c6a94e6a2c62addbe7125f36c1595","tid":1638033,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:31:17.000Z","msg":"又反送中，又燒舖，又打爛交通燈，又打爛港鐵，又撞車，警察打死無辜市民，示威者又打人，黑社會又打人，警黑合作勾結，香港根本係內亂。<br />\n<br />\n除左反修例外，港交所又收購失敗，沙中線醜聞。<br />\n<br />\n股市和樓市咁都冇大跌，唯一解釋，就係中共中央出重手，入市干預。<br />\n<br />\n樓市仲要係陰跌，唔係中共政府干預力量，解釋唔到。<br />\n<br />\n香港崇尚自由市場，香港政府不會主動干預市場。<br />\n但香港無法控制其他政府（如中共中央人民政府）的干預。"},{"pid":"ad9cd46a8c364b0379c750c41c28e6a1790ae629","tid":1638033,"uid":54511,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你今日先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中資股 占恆生指數成份65-70% （唔係點控制你股市）<br />\n樓市 都一樣 所有 有官 都渣緊幾十層 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee57a38c875076231083716438cda6fa1f10314c","tid":1638033,"uid":29620,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:36:11.000Z","msg":"地鐵都唔大跌<br />\n好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d8b186d02f830f47825a6863d6017ecd4f8d0d","tid":1638033,"uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:37:29.000Z","msg":"真的警察國家！中共維穩經費達6.3兆 比軍費還高<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2722781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2722781&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNqGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=03ac69ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2722781&h=228f520d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2722781</a>"},{"pid":"49e